title: Program
---
description: The schedule of the Swiss Python Summit
---
ordering: 3
---
body:

# Program 2026

The detailed program is expected to be announced in July.

- **Thursday 22th October:** Day 1 - Python, the programming language you love
  - This day is all about general Python topics and the programming language you love. Discover the wide field of Python applications, hear how others use the language, and meet Swiss Pythonistas.
- **Friday 23th October:** Day 2 - Data Science & more
  - This day is specially dedicated to all Data Science related topics such as Machine Learning, Data Processing & Analytics, Data Engineering, Data Visualization, AI, LLM and many more ...

🔔 Stay tuned and following us on our social media channels on [Linkedin](https://www.linkedin.com/company/swiss-python-summit) and [X](https://x.com/pythonsummit) for updates.

🎥 Take a look at our [recordings](/recordings) and explore what was covered in previous summits.